<subSubSection pageId="169" pageNumber="170" type="distinguishing features">
<paragraph pageId="169" pageNumber="170">Distinguishing features.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="169" pageNumber="170">
Distinguished by its rigid, more or less fastigiate habit, the branches all woody. Leaves are linear, 1-1.5 
<normalizedToken originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
0.2 cm and mostly absent below. The hairs on the bracteoles and calyx are shorter than in the type.
</paragraph>
